Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:36.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶  貴志  你來看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.56,0:01:37.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
